HON. KEITH ELLISON

                              of minnesota

                    in the house of representatives

                       Tuesday, November 14, 2017
content.speaker: None

content.text:
Mr. ELLISON. Mr. Speaker, due to other commitments, I missed the 
following Roll Call votes. Had I been present, on Roll Call no. 613, I 
would have voted yes; and on Roll Call no. 614, I would have voted no.
